metadata.name: Dreamer 1
metadata.description:
Creating a large scale AI project that has variety, interesting traits, and appealing looks while also including a human artist into the original training dataset has been an exploration.

Just like the cubism movement, this collection is not meant to be a perfect representation of human form but a celebration of the wonderfully weird ways that art and AI meet to push the edge of art history. Much like our human inputs, the Dreamers and their AI assigned traits aren't perfect.
